{"type": "article", "id": 25721, "title": "DIY 树枝灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-21T06:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 81, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162633t7zW2biV9mQfRyEq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">纽约布鲁克林的两位设计师 <a href=\"http://jasonkrugman.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://jasonkrugman.com/', 'Jason Krugman');\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Krugman</a> 和 <a href=\"http://scottleinweber.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://scottleinweber.com/', 'Scott Leinweber');\" target=\"_blank\">Scott Leinweber</a> 共同推出了这款名为 Splyt Light 的模块式灯具，它由几种不同造型的配件构成，让你可以自己动手设计出独一无二的“树枝灯”——你只需要搭出想要的造型，再安上灯泡就行了。你可以在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1244118214/splyt-light\">Kickstarter</a> 上看到更多的相关信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162631CtOVWR7u5Jn6y4eK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021626325kAHtmfxQOpqITdr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021626322aY4PzBgnKJrhXAI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162633S7FwxZoWnXAE24C0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}